<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>つきじしょくどう·一虎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">筑地食堂•一虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">火爆广州的日式丼饭【筑地食堂•一虎】</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">第二家店来了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">以「日式居酒屋」为主题！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">匠心制作“日式烧鸟”</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在「渔船上的居酒屋」吃地道的日式料理</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">带你一秒闪现东京街头！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200822/c6bf994c3d7b4affa0bd33e9c09ad64e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200822/d2ebbdf8bd0e46818419439404813f00.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200822/19add67f0739420880ad82618a12252b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/在法律范围内，活动解释权归商家所有/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200822/19add67f0739420880ad82618a12252b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200822/40c92619e6cf4ad4adb09fd245c1783d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200822/8224fba25466435dbee3f696fe3b21c8.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200822/1940914461ed461a94a894cfa59aac09.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200822/8cf64025651c498c9d5f50142c6eb133.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200822/8c3d40b6e47b4be19542e417931e3d7b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200822/fcc05b70817840c495e0741240b5bff2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>つきじしょくどう·一虎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">火爆正佳的<strong>『筑地食堂•一虎』</strong>，以日式丼饭获得顾客的喜爱，现在第二家来了！就在五号停机坪！<strong>现推出匠心制作的“日式烧鸟”！</strong>精选新鲜时令鱼贝蔬果，优质食材，为顾客带来鱼获宝地“筑地市场”的惊喜！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 私藏的“烧鸟酒馆” ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200822/abeb4b5e720448b1a696f1ce8cc62735.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>以「日式居酒屋」为主题的『一虎』，不仅是一间日式丼饭，还是一件充满人间烟火的“烧鸟酒馆”。</strong>正宗的日式烧鸟，性价比超高！精选优质的食材，采用地道的日式烹饪手法烧制。再配上一小杯日本清酒，仿佛自己就是日剧里的主人公。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200822/7f477aaf7179481dab2cdf71482b4ba1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200822/a55fe6a5362a40399eaad8971b1ba106.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 吃烧鸟，这里做到了极致 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">□□□□</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200822/9282fdcb0be545ba8a61d832e3cd6399.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">×××</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200822/abeb4b5e720448b1a696f1ce8cc62735.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">烧鸟就有鸡翅、冬菇、软骨、鸡肾、鸡心、圆椒那么多种！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200822/612f941869c34e5687ed28ec1eb6eda0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200822/041e1be7bc3c4b499580d9254a75ee91.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200822/7baf9592b9144e0d92f9b55fa48a45aa.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200822/9a2357b403a94bc5a29e7663abb41697.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200822/1dcfff384b3d48c685a98ae24b581841.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>烤物其实很考验厨师的技巧，每一串烧物的火候，烤制时间都由师傅把控，不差分毫。</strong>油脂滴落在烤炉上，产生的烟熏味和勐火使得烤出来的食材更有烧烤的味道，这是烤物的精髓所在。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200822/469ba366f0014142a93329b30abb8169.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200822/05e4dc948c2749a69b5ad8732cfa3e4c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最后撒上盐和胡椒粉，使得食材更入味，就完成了。<strong>烤肉的香味很浓郁，外表面焦香十足，里面却鲜嫩多汁，极其诱人！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200822/86d170a8909a456f8b1d7fc796d9422b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200822/ccfd21d82dc2417491f17c40e6151fe2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200822/1f785a54f90b4fbf83497fc577d63374.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200822/1fc6f71c5ce043d6b10810d8d2f876e8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200822/53656100b8c046a88387740b3b557cc0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200822/e219e02424d54f72921b0e8c8d706e0d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">烤内脏很能体验出一家店的烧鸟水平，『一虎』的鸡肾<strong>软嫩中带点生硬，表皮焦香，还能保持到食材原本的新鲜度。</strong>烤鸡翅呈金黄色，<strong>外皮烤焦，里面的肉鲜嫩十足！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 花鱼一夜干 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200822/213c9ef70ff14bb5929d8893703b6a0e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200822/7126d009e46f4f36b4393b8fa8caa914.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">腌制后的花鱼十分入味，先是大火烤制，<strong>瞬间把鱼的水分牢牢锁住，发出阵阵香味，</strong>闻到都在咽口水了...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200822/e91eefe0fb9d4a63822c55bb3a5a3ea1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200822/a8ea6e453cf04c1ab4c5615ad0916ee4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200822/d3d96820420d4342986ae917ed266922.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200822/e964ba7e6e444dcd9ffa4267344f29aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>鱼皮和鱼肉表面烤得金黄，但是里面的鱼肉依然细腻鲜嫩。</strong>咸鲜味十足，作为下酒菜，简直一流！蘸上蛋黄酱吃，中和了一点鱼的咸味，别有一番风味~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 多春鱼&amp;茄子 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200822/9037578f6f6745488b4d03ad901cc549.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200822/3d7b998919384d92b810cb92061d43ac.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200822/926900f1c6b54c9885741e2ecec4a15a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200822/ba47122cca0a4267ba8bf16c15766bcc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">烤多春鱼也一定不能错过，这里的多春鱼，鱼籽很多。<strong>一口下去，鱼的外表皮焦香中带点软嫩，鱼籽在口中爆发，口感很过瘾。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200822/a730ca88c9e248699786ea99930a2031.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200822/b491c1f81d904af58a09fe42a0412c34.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200822/f6205346f62848d6942454ab12864a9c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200822/50d26ba132c84a10b6d51699375e692c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">烤茄子采用新鲜现切的茄子，<strong>独特日式烤法，口感软糯，微咸带点鲜甜，一口就爱上了！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 土豆沙拉 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200822/551f2bcd8a5a41568f4bb20be4343dac.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200822/6e7746ebea0e4b69bc54fbcdea329449.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>土豆沙拉用料十足，集土豆、蟹子、新鲜青瓜、松子、薯片和蔬菜于一身。</strong>土豆有一股淡淡的奶香味，口感粘稠，配上爽口的蟹子与松子，口感丰富，<strong>是许多回头客的心头好！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200822/d3d6d603862748e2a3d0a9c75477ef5e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有一种独特的吃法，用薯片装上沙拉，直接一口吃下。<strong>口感丰富的沙拉中多了一份薯片的香脆，别有一番风味！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 鳗鱼炒饭 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200822/2dfe9520f03e4a2d9106246385ac3b48.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200822/3c75906769094de7baac3e42a523306b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">采用蒲烧鳗鱼与调好味的寿司饭一起翻炒，再淋上蒲烧酱汁，使得炒饭更入味。<strong>鳗鱼的鲜、酱汁的香完全渗入米饭中，一口入魂！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 小吃&amp;饮品 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200822/f400e246391c4210ad71e1210e998772.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200822/e246a946e23a4eda88344154f15f5f8b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200822/b7b4f938fcbc443a8ab0cdf27c526dc8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">除了烧鸟、烤物等，还有多汁入味又带点微辣的毛豆，和啤酒、可尔必思。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200822/4fbafdedd7534147a6c17a93eaba2391.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200822/dfc34799f49d43cca5694199f47e3e10.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 藏在闹市的「日式居酒屋」 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">□□□□</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200822/87f1bd7862174360b52d739284ddfa0a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200822/41e539084b3d4aafbe63163191e13172.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200822/c46087504fdd4aee994c4aa9a0837f4f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200822/4a92532be1064521bbefaa689ca9fb0e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一进入店里，浓浓的和风日式氛围把你环绕，仿佛瞬间穿越到东京街头！</strong>暖色系日式古拙和风配上原木风桌椅，显得格外温馨别致。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200822/014e0da581194f49833b39d3a40c6f54.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200822/6dcef9b249bf4fdc880bcaf1bd43dbef.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>つきじしょくどう·一虎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200822/2622639c3e4f46af8453bf00597c0177.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>日式纸灯笼、木头阶梯、日式海报还有琳琅满目的和风元素点缀，随便一拍都是日系大片！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▨ 渔船上的居酒屋水吧 ▨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200822/ec52140db0c14173a407d5d891f0a8dd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200822/eb3e3a8fa6a44a6c9fb4aa26b32c1fc0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200822/aa71a720b86e4d80bab7bc17acd1b1f4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>开放式水吧还原江户时期渔船的造型，</strong>船的中间是供店员现场制作酒水、饮品的，船的边缘是用餐区，充满日料那种纯粹、原始的氛围，<strong>仿佛穿越到日本的江户时期。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200822/2f29eafeee624c67adf6ad7a4b2c0730.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200822/2a2d5aa29f4c4f01bb4bbc2cf2f2b883.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200822/fcc05b70817840c495e0741240b5bff2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">1</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这<strong>里很适合聚会、聊天，带上三五知己一边吃着正宗的日式烧鸟料理，一边把酒畅谈。</strong>心情都被治愈了，所有烦恼统统都没有了~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200822/d2ebbdf8bd0e46818419439404813f00.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200822/19add67f0739420880ad82618a12252b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">*仅限五号停机坪店可用*</p>
